<p style="color:gray">DELIVERY TO C.LVIV</p>
<hr>
Delivery is carried out on working days from 9.00-18.00.<br><br>

When placing an order before 15.00 a delivery is carried out on the next business day, when placing an order after 15.00 delivery is carried out one business day.
 In non-cash payment - delivery within 2 working days after receipt of money.<br><br>

When ordering for more than UAH 500 - delivery is free of charge.<br><br>

When ordering for the amount less than 500 UAH - the cost of delivery is 50 UAH.<br><br><br>


<p style="color:gray">DELIVERY TO UKRAINE</p>
<hr>
Delivery is carried out only when subscribing for the ordered goods.<br><br>

Delivery is carried out by the transportation service Novaya Poshta or other carriers (in agreement with the customer) in the term from two to three working days; the delivery is paid by the customer according to the carrier's fares. <br><br><br>



